conf/ repository

file			description
------------------------------------------------------
release			the current main trunk version
			$major.$minor$n where $n is (A .. Z).

release_version		the snapshot version	(cvs ignore this)

mode			null (default) or "daily"

branch			"current" or "stable"


[DESCRIPTION]

conf/release_version is updated when "make snapshot" runs. I ignore
conf/release_version which file has current snapshot number but the
information is not needed.
